                            <comment id="370239" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 22 Apr 2023 17:30:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&quot; merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50415/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/50415/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16666&quot; title=&quot;Remove or update Doxygen files&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16666&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16666&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; doc: remove unmaintained doxyfiles&lt;br/&gt;
